name: Cube Dash (OscarStirling)
description:
Cube Dash is a game where you control a cube and have to get him to the other side without dying. You die if you run into red enemies or if you just fall off. Move with 'a' and 'd'.

Special thanks to Brackey on youtube for the help. Go support him. I also got the music from HeatlyBros on youtube.
